{"TopicId":162592,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Hot Staging","CreatedByName":"DJ Reonic","CreatedById":161437,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-27T19:01:46Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DJ Reonic","CreatedById":161437,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-27T19:01:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone tried hot-staging in KSP? Is it even possible to do without destroying the rocket trying to do it? I\u0027ve been trying to get something working with Tantares, but I keep blowing stuff up. I\u0027m thinking of just using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E configs to edit Max temps and such on the proper parts. Any ideas?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-27T19:11:38Z\u0022 title=\u002206/27/2017 07:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by DJ Reonic\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-27T19:52:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would probably be the best thing to do, edit part temps.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-27T19:54:38Z\u0022 title=\u002206/27/2017 07:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by regex\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sebi.zzr","CreatedById":81294,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-27T19:58:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223104598\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221498590106\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161437\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DJ Reonic\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, DJ Reonic said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny ideas?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry to play with:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EMODULE\n{\n name = ModuleEngines\n exhaustDamageDistanceOffset = \n}\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-27T22:28:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223104598\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221498590106\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161437\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DJ Reonic\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, DJ Reonic said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone tried hot-staging in KSP? Is it even possible to do without destroying the rocket trying to do it? I\u0027ve been trying to get something working with Tantares, but I keep blowing stuff up. I\u0027m thinking of just using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E configs to edit Max temps and such on the proper parts. Any ideas?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if it would be possible to add a heat shield to at lest temporarily keep stuff from exploding. Never played with tantares though....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DJ Reonic","CreatedById":161437,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-28T15:12:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223104794\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221498602523\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160994\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qzgy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, qzgy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if it would be possible to add a heat shield to at lest temporarily keep stuff from exploding. Never played with tantares though....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m going to try doing that along with some offsetting, to see if i can come up with something. I\u0027ll try using Smart Parts to control the staging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"genericeventhandler","CreatedById":149557,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-29T08:11:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223105382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221498662777\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161437\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DJ Reonic\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, DJ Reonic said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m going to try doing that along with some offsetting, to see if i can come up with something. I\u0027ll try using Smart Parts to control the staging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe part module you need is Stager, \u00A0I can\u0027t test this because as usual I am at work \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would try copying a decoupler and see if it works.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@PART[somepartnameHere]:NEEDS[SmartParts]:FINAL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n{\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 MODULE\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n{\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nname = Stager\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nactivationPercentage = 0.01 // not sure if this is 1 or 0.01 as a percentage\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmonitoredResource = LiquidFuel\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ngroup = 0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n}\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n}\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGEH.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}